Log in to GitHub.
Click the + icon in the upper-right corner and select New repository.
Give your repository a name.
[Important]: Leave "Add a README", ".gitignore", and "License" unchecked to prevent initial conflicts.
Click Create repository.
Copy the HTTPS or SSH URL provided on the quick-setup screen (e.g., https://github.com)

git init // initialize git in the project folder
git branch -M main  //Set your default branch name to main
git remote add origin PASTE_YOUR_COPIED_URL_HERE //Link the local project to github
git add . // stage all your files
git commit -m "Initial commit" //First local commit
git push -u origin main  //Push the code.(The -u flag links your local branch to the remote branch so you can simply type git push next time.



npm new <project_name>
Follow the below project structure:
src/app/
├── core/                  # App-wide singleton items (loaded once)
│   ├── guards/            # Route guards (e.g., auth.guard.ts)
│   ├── interceptors/      # HTTP interceptors (e.g., jwt.interceptor.ts)
│   ├── services/          # Global services (e.g., theme.service.ts)
│   └── models/            # Global TypeScript interfaces/types
│
├── shared/                # Reusable building blocks across features
│   ├── components/        # Dumb/reusable UI components (buttons, cards)
│   ├── directives/        # Custom directives
│   ├── pipes/             # Custom pipes
│   └── utils/             # Helper/utility functions
│
├── features/              # Feature-based modules (lazy-loaded routes)
│   ├── dashboard/         # Example feature folder
│   │   ├── components/    # Feature-specific child components
│   │   ├── services/      # Feature-specific services/APIs
│   │   ├── models/        # Feature-specific data interfaces
│   │   └── dashboard.routes.ts
│   │
│   └── auth/              # Another feature (login, register)
│
├── layout/                # Skeleton structure of the application
│   ├── header/            # Navigation header component
│   ├── footer/            # Footer component
│   └── sidebar/           # Sidebar menu component
│
├── app.component.ts       # Root component
├── app.config.ts          # Global application providers & config
└── app.routes.ts          # Main application routing


